name: Dedos e têmporas #2
description:
Divided into two parts, this piece contains a soundscape recorded by the lake in the Cerrado of Tocantins. This track was exclusively composed and recorded to be an NFT. Only voice and acoustic guitar, no digital processing into mixing, giving you the experience of being on the recording set. 
Recorded by Gabriel Worm. 
Song by Luzo Cairo and Luís Felipe.
